Nerdfonts
---------
https://nerdfonts.com/

Script
------
Script downloads Nerd font ttf files and install configuration file for the fontconfig
which adds preference for the symbols from Nerd font for common fonts.

Configuration file taken from
https://github.com/ryanoasis/nerd-fonts/blob/master/10-nerd-font-symbols.conf
and adjusted to support Hack font.
